br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n關於我地既報導：<br />\n眾新聞：I Banker（虛構）與網民發起逢周五、日罷買：零成本，希望和理非響應<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zpstHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zpstHS&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=39c420ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zpstHS</a><br />\nＳＣＭＰ既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7zPJC&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=a4e5568c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1ta7DfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ta7DfO.jpg&h=470d5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5OkGHHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OkGHHu.jpg&h=ee06cc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0&amp;oe=5DD82060\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0%26oe%3D5DD82060&h=80325f8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed378eef619fe5b4b67cb6bb349210d57330b590","tid":1516710,"u